        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[#经常掰手指会得关节炎吗##掰手指会伤关节吗#？[ok][NO][haha][来]手指关节的连接处，有一个关节囊，里面充满滑膜液，它是在关节变直或变弯时起润滑作用。另外，...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%8E%B0%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E7%82%8E%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%8E%B0%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E7%82%8E%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常掰手指会得关节炎吗#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8E%B0%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A4%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8E%B0%E6%89%8B%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A4%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#掰手指会伤关节吗#</span></a>？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[ok]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_ok-2fdfaf8847.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[NO]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_buyao-3a904f27f5.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[haha]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_haha-dd41b13682.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[来]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_lai-da75e9a8cc.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>手指关节的连接处，有一个关节囊，里面充满滑膜液，它是在关节变直或变弯时起润滑作用。另外，关节周围还有肌腱，关节活动时会收缩和延长。<br><br>当你掰手指的时候，关节囊被拉伸和挤压，肌腱会在关节骨突的地方滑动，互相摩擦和急剧地活动，就会发出“砰”的弹响声音。<br><br>经常掰手指，会掰成关节炎吗？想多了。但如果用力过猛，有可能造成关节周围韧带肌腱的急性损伤，或者关节错位。经常掰手指，还会引起关节松弛，并且削弱你的握力，严重的还会出现心理问题。<br><br>所以，有事没事别掰手指<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcumcn5676j2064064aag.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
